rows.label: qst104502_msg003
rows.name: Please fetch it for me, mo.

rows.label: qst104502_msg0002
rows.name:
We'll open our shop at the
Superbian Garrison you can
see from here, mo!

rows.label: qst104502_msg0003
rows.name: We can't celebrate just yet, mo.

rows.label: qst104502_msg0004
rows.name:
Sniff-sniff... I smell a
formidable monster, mo!

rows.label: qst104502_msg0005
rows.name:
An Arman Balgas! That thing is
scary, mo! It'll eat us up, mo!

rows.label: qst104502_msg0006
rows.name:
If you defeat about three of
them, we should be able to make
our way there safely, mo.

rows.label: qst104502_msg0008
rows.name:
I'll be watching from here to see if
you've defeated them. When I think it's
okay, we'll run to the garrison, mo.

rows.label: qst104502_msg0101
rows.name: Please defeat three Arman Balgas, mo.

rows.label: qst104502_msg0102
rows.name:
The moment you defeat them, we'll
all make a run for it, mo.

rows.label: qst104502_msg0103
rows.name:
We'll meet at the
Superbian Garrison, mo!
